    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Decopin&quot; is a traditional Japanese &quot;Flick&quot; action to express friendliness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Flick, flick, flick... Click, click, click... Decopins is a tower defense like game with simple action. Don't let Donuts escape from your donuts shop by clicking and Magic. 20 stages, Hell/Death mode and bonus stage. Level up your Decopin skill and make full use of MAGIC.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't think difficult. Just clicking and clicking Donuts!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*&quot;Decopin&quot; means Flick or Click in Japanese.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*Don't do Decopin or use Magic in real world, thankyou.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*Gamepad(XInput), Mouse and Keyboard controls are supported.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*Mouse aiming is more confortable.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*Decopins2 will be launched on Jan, 2024.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Credits:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Music:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > &quot;Cassette Tape Dream&quot; Main Music, Sharou</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > &quot;Gentle Distance&quot; Stage Over, Anonyment</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > &quot;Old Blood&quot; Stage 15, Kohrogi</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > &quot;Funk Style&quot; Inventry Music, Phalene</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > &quot;Automata&quot; Stage 20, Low</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > &quot;Acogi POP&quot; Chill Out Infinity, Br'z</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > &quot;FUNK JAZZ FUSION Fu&quot; Hell Mode, Keisuke Ito</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > &quot;Chill the sun&quot;, STAGE 5, Tagord</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SE: Koukaon-Labo</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thankyou for Fanstasic Musics, Fantastic SE, Fantastic 3D Assets and All Players!</p>",
